00:30:31.638 --> 00:30:35.058
pertuzumab, which started in 2012 in HER2 positive

513
00:30:35.138 --> 00:30:38.548
metastatic breast cancer and all through to 2020.

514
00:30:38.938 --> 00:30:42.758
And so in the zenatuximab discovery started in 2013, so

515
00:30:42.798 --> 00:30:46.458
shortly after and during the first two approvals of trastuzumab in

516
00:30:46.518 --> 00:30:48.978
combination with pertuzumab in breast cancer.

